What did I do? Don't touch me!

537
00:42:20,623 --> 00:42:22,625
I won't touch you. Get out.

538
00:42:24,293 --> 00:42:27,755
I won't leave till I get what I deserve!

539
00:42:27,922 --> 00:42:30,633
What you deserve is for me to kick you out.

540
00:42:30,799 --> 00:42:33,761
Because of her I won't.

541
00:42:33,928 --> 00:42:37,765
Get out!
I'm doing you a favor by throwing you out.

542
00:42:37,973 --> 00:42:40,517
Tell me what's happened to him.

543
00:42:40,976 --> 00:42:42,686
It's my house, I want you out.

544
00:42:42,853 --> 00:42:45,314
Fine, but it's not right.

545
00:42:45,814 --> 00:42:47,775
- It displeases God.
- Out!

546
00:42:48,817 --> 00:42:50,319
That's it.

547
00:42:53,614 --> 00:42:54,657
Dad.

548
00:43:05,334 --> 00:43:07,962
Open the door. It's me.
I want to come in...

549
00:43:09,630 --> 00:43:11,674
This is how you watch him?

550
00:43:15,552 --> 00:43:17,054
Open the door.

551
00:43:18,514 --> 00:43:20,557
Go check what's behind you.

552
00:43:21,016 --> 00:43:22,184
Have a look.

553
00:43:23,852 --> 00:43:24,852
Open the door!

554
00:43:24,895 --> 00:43:27,189
It's no use shouting.

555
00:43:28,148 --> 00:43:30,859
This is why I asked you to watch him.

556
00:43:31,026 --> 00:43:33,654
Maybe his leg hurts and he can't get up.

557
00:43:34,530 --> 00:43:36,573
Grandpa...

558
00:43:38,742 --> 00:43:41,078
Dad, open the door.

559
00:43:41,870 --> 00:43:43,998
Open the door, please.

560
00:43:45,749 --> 00:43:48,168
I'm going to push the door open.

561
00:43:48,335 --> 00:43:51,880
It'll hit you, Dad. Move aside.

562
00:43:53,882 --> 00:43:56,844
I'm going to push the door open.

563
00:43:59,555 --> 00:44:02,391
Why do you do this to yourself?

564
00:44:15,195 --> 00:44:16,572
Who told you to come in?

565
00:44:16,739 --> 00:44:19,533
- What happened to him?
- Give me the key. Get out!

566
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:20,909
I didn't steal from you.

567
00:44:21,076 --> 00:44:22,786
You are pissing me off!

568
00:44:22,870 --> 00:44:23,870
I didn't.

569
00:44:23,912 --> 00:44:27,708
- Don't give me that!
- I wouldn't be here now if I had.

570
00:44:27,875 --> 00:44:28,876
Get out.

571
00:44:28,959 --> 00:44:30,461
Pay me for today.

572
00:44:30,586 --> 00:44:33,589
You already took your pay, didn't you?

573
00:44:34,298 --> 00:44:38,427
Since 5:30 this morning
with my daughter... Somayeh!

574
00:44:38,719 --> 00:44:39,928
Sir, wait!

575
00:44:40,095 --> 00:44:41,430
Get out.

576
00:44:41,597 --> 00:44:45,100
I swear I didn't steal.

577
00:44:45,267 --> 00:44:46,769
Get out!

578
00:44:59,573 --> 00:45:00,574
What happened?

579
00:45:05,412 --> 00:45:06,747
What happened?

580
00:45:07,122 --> 00:45:08,457
Sit.

581
00:45:16,006 --> 00:45:17,508
What happened?

582
00:45:20,928 --> 00:45:22,805
Mommy, be careful.

583
00:46:34,668 --> 00:46:36,545
Tell her to work with you on your English.

584
00:46:36,712 --> 00:46:37,838
Bye, Grandpa.

585
00:46:38,589 --> 00:46:40,757
Dad, Termeh said bye.

586
00:46:44,511 --> 00:46:45,596
Careful!

587
00:46:51,351 --> 00:46:52,436
Okay.

588
00:46:55,522 --> 00:46:56,607
What is it?

589
00:46:56,773 --> 00:46:58,108
Mom says come in.

590
00:46:59,193 --> 00:47:00,944
Tell her Grandpa's in the car.

591
00:47:01,111 --> 00:47:02,362
She says it's important.

592
00:47:05,532 --> 00:47:08,952
Not divorced yet and already ignoring us!

593
00:47:09,119 --> 00:47:10,579
I'm busy.

594
00:47:10,954 --> 00:47:14,082
People divorce their
wives to get less busy.

595
00:47:14,249 --> 00:47:17,127
Ma'am, these channels have too much static.

596
00:47:17,294 --> 00:47:19,254
Okay, set the ones you can.

597
00:47:20,547 --> 00:47:22,591
- Come and sit.
- Thank you. Simin...

598
00:47:27,930 --> 00:47:28,931
Hi.

599
00:47:31,767 --> 00:47:33,268
Where's Termeh?

600
00:47:33,894 --> 00:47:35,270
In the car with dad.

601
00:47:35,479 --> 00:47:37,105
Then bring him in, too.

602
00:47:37,481 --> 00:47:38,941
No, he is tired.

603
00:47:39,107 --> 00:47:40,400
It's his nap time.

604
00:47:42,277 --> 00:47:43,278
What is it?

605
00:47:43,946 --> 00:47:45,614
Did you have a fight with that woman?

606
00:47:46,823 --> 00:47:47,908
Did she come see you?

607
00:47:48,116 --> 00:47:49,159
Her sister-in-law called.

608
00:47:49,952 --> 00:47:51,620
Shameless!

609
00:47:51,787 --> 00:47:52,955
What did she do?

610
00:47:53,121 --> 00:47:56,500
Tied the old man to the bed
and locked the door.

611
00:47:56,667 --> 00:47:58,335
Went after her own errands.

612
00:47:58,794 --> 00:48:01,338
If I'd gotten there 10 minutes later,
I would've lost him.

613
00:48:01,421 --> 00:48:02,714
Is he okay?

614
00:48:02,798 --> 00:48:04,007
He had fallen off the bed.

615
00:48:04,174 --> 00:48:06,635
I don't know for how long he was like that.

616
00:48:07,010 --> 00:48:08,053
Where had she gone?

617
00:48:08,136 --> 00:48:09,137
How should I know?

618
00:48:09,846 --> 00:48:10,973
She said you hit her.

619
00:48:11,515 --> 00:48:12,558
I hit her?

620
00:48:13,100 --> 00:48:15,602
- Nonsense.
- Then why is she in the hospital?

621
00:48:17,938 --> 00:48:19,815
Hospital? Why?

622
00:48:20,649 --> 00:48:22,025
You're asking me?

623
00:48:22,276 --> 00:48:23,777
I just pushed her out of the house.

624
00:48:23,944 --> 00:48:26,196
The sister-in-law called and told me off.

625
00:48:26,989 --> 00:48:27,990
Saying what?

626
00:48:28,198 --> 00:48:30,951
That if she dies,
her blood will be on your hands.

627
00:48:32,995 --> 00:48:33,996
Stuff like that.

628
00:48:35,706 --> 00:48:40,544
- She didn't say what happened?
- I hung up. She started cursing.

629
00:48:43,547 --> 00:48:46,633
That's what you get
for hiring people off the streets.

630
00:48:46,800 --> 00:48:51,054
Don't blame me.
I told you I only know her sister-in-law.

631
00:48:51,221 --> 00:48:53,015
Did she say which hospital?

632
00:48:58,520 --> 00:48:59,688
- Hello.
- Yes?

633
00:49:00,689 --> 00:49:01,857
Hold, please.

634
00:49:02,357 --> 00:49:05,902
A woman by the name of Razieh was
brought in tonight.

635
00:49:06,236 --> 00:49:09,698
- What's her family name?
- I don't know. She was admitted earlier.

636
00:49:09,865 --> 00:49:11,033
Why was she brought in?

637
00:49:11,199 --> 00:49:13,994
- They just told us...
- That she was taken to hospital.

638
00:49:14,494 --> 00:49:16,872
I'll call you back. Bye.

639
00:49:17,205 --> 00:49:20,167
Her husband's last name is Samadi.

640
00:49:24,379 --> 00:49:26,006
Razieh Asnaqi?

641
00:49:26,548 --> 00:49:28,717
Is she in her thirties?

642
00:49:31,053 --> 00:49:32,721
She had surgery. She's in post-op.

643
00:49:33,221 --> 00:49:34,306
Why surgery?

644
00:49:35,349 --> 00:49:36,600
She had a miscarriage.

645
00:49:40,520 --> 00:49:41,605
Is she okay now?

646
00:49:41,688 --> 00:49:42,939
Hello? Hold.

647
00:49:43,023 --> 00:49:44,024
Yes.

648
00:49:44,107 --> 00:49:46,943
Is her family here?

649
00:49:47,194 --> 00:49:48,514
If they are, they are downstairs.

650
00:49:48,904 --> 00:49:50,197
Thank you.

651
00:49:57,537 --> 00:49:59,247
What did you do to her?

652
00:50:01,083 --> 00:50:02,626
What did I do to her?

653
00:50:23,230 --> 00:50:24,231
Hello.

654
00:50:28,110 --> 00:50:29,611
- How are you?
- Fine, thanks.

655
00:50:29,820 --> 00:50:30,946
Hello, ma'am.

656
00:50:31,321 --> 00:50:32,322
How is she?

657
00:50:32,948 --> 00:50:33,949
Who?

658
00:50:34,616 --> 00:50:35,826
Your wife.

659
00:50:37,119 --> 00:50:38,829
They took her to the ward.

660
00:50:40,330 --> 00:50:41,623
Do you know her?

661
00:50:41,790 --> 00:50:43,959
- I know her.
- My wife.

662
00:50:44,292 --> 00:50:46,795
- They didn't have sandwiches.
- Hello.

663
00:50:53,260 --> 00:50:54,928
Can we see her?

664
00:50:55,095 --> 00:50:57,013
Where do you know her from?

665
00:50:57,305 --> 00:51:01,309
Your sister introduced her to us
for housework.

666
00:51:01,518 --> 00:51:03,103
Thanks a lot!

667
00:51:05,605 --> 00:51:07,085
She was coming to your house to work?

668
00:51:07,441 --> 00:51:08,817
She came for a few days.

669
00:51:09,484 --> 00:51:12,487
Apparently you couldn't come
so she came in your place.

670
00:51:12,696 --> 00:51:14,364
Come sit and eat something.

671
00:51:14,656 --> 00:51:17,659
You mean she took care of your father?

672
00:51:17,993 --> 00:51:19,619
Just for a few days.

673
00:51:20,162 --> 00:51:21,496
Two or three days.

674
00:51:21,663 --> 00:51:24,332
Why didn't you tell me this at the bank?

675
00:51:26,710 --> 00:51:28,712
I thought she would tell you.

676
00:51:29,963 --> 00:51:31,715
Why have you come here now?

677
00:51:31,882 --> 00:51:33,800
To see if we can do something.

678
00:51:33,967 --> 00:51:34,968
Do what?

679
00:51:35,135 --> 00:51:37,637
Help. We were worried.

680
00:51:37,804 --> 00:51:39,347
Did she fall?

681
00:51:40,015 --> 00:51:42,476
Come with me. I'll explain.

682
00:51:43,310 --> 00:51:45,854
I'll explain to you... Come with me.

683
00:51:46,354 --> 00:51:48,523
I understand your situation.

684
00:51:48,690 --> 00:51:51,693
You kill her child
and now you've come to do what?

685
00:51:51,860 --> 00:51:52,986
I'm really sorry.

686
00:51:53,153 --> 00:51:55,655
I'm sorry won't be a child to her.

687
00:51:55,864 --> 00:51:57,365
Just tell me one thing.

688
00:51:57,532 --> 00:51:58,992
I'll explain outside.

689
00:51:59,367 --> 00:52:01,870
Wait! Why didn't you tell me that day?

690
00:52:02,329 --> 00:52:04,080
I told you. I thought she...

691
00:52:07,417 --> 00:52:09,920
You live alone in that house.

692
00:52:11,880 --> 00:52:13,548
Let him go.

693
00:52:14,382 --> 00:52:15,884
Calm down.

694
00:52:16,927 --> 00:52:19,221
This is a hospital.

695
00:52:20,889 --> 00:52:22,182
Don't!

696
00:52:22,349 --> 00:52:23,350
Stop!

697
00:52:27,771 --> 00:52:29,856
Why the hell did you come here?

698
00:52:33,276 --> 00:52:34,861
Let me see.

699
00:52:35,403 --> 00:52:37,656
- My own sister?
- I'm sorry.

700
00:52:37,739 --> 00:52:38,782
Forgive me.

701
00:52:38,865 --> 00:52:39,866
Let me see.

702
00:52:43,745 --> 00:52:45,705
Come out here.

703
00:52:47,415 --> 00:52:48,416
I want to talk to you.

704
00:52:51,461 --> 00:52:53,588
Please, I beg you. Hojjat!

705
00:53:01,304 --> 00:53:04,099
Do you want your seat down?

706
00:53:04,432 --> 00:53:05,433
No.

707
00:53:06,810 --> 00:53:10,105
I'll take you home
then I'll get Dad and Termeh.

708
00:53:11,773 --> 00:53:12,983
No.

709
00:53:14,442 --> 00:53:15,777
No?

710
00:53:16,987 --> 00:53:19,739
You want to go to your parents' like this?

711
00:53:21,449 --> 00:53:24,160
It's over. You're coming home tonight.

712
00:53:27,247 --> 00:53:28,290
I don't want to.

713
00:53:38,633 --> 00:53:40,135
Where are you going?

714
00:53:47,475 --> 00:53:48,518
Cell phone.

715
00:53:50,103 --> 00:53:51,479
Hand it in.

716
00:55:00,715 --> 00:55:02,884
Did you hear his complaint?

717
00:55:03,051 --> 00:55:04,260
It was the 13th.

718
00:55:05,345 --> 00:55:07,931
I'm sorry. I was really upset when I heard.

719
00:55:08,181 --> 00:55:10,684
- I went to the hospital.
- Then you admit it.

720
00:55:12,268 --> 00:55:13,979
Is this the medical examiner's report?

721
00:55:14,062 --> 00:55:18,525
It is the hospital report that we took

722
00:55:18,692 --> 00:55:20,694
to the medical examiner.

723
00:55:20,860 --> 00:55:22,487
Four and half months, male.

724
00:55:22,570 --> 00:55:23,905
Please explain.

725
00:55:24,364 --> 00:55:26,574
I accept that I was a bit rough.

726
00:55:26,741 --> 00:55:28,410
By rough you mean you pushed her?

727
00:55:28,618 --> 00:55:31,621
No. I tried to get her out of my house.

728
00:55:32,747 --> 00:55:35,291
Be clear. Your charge is murder.

729
00:55:36,459 --> 00:55:39,129
It was 19 weeks old. A full human being.

730
00:55:40,755 --> 00:55:43,133
I didn't intend to push her.

731
00:55:43,299 --> 00:55:45,593
I wanted her to leave
so I could close the door.

732
00:55:45,760 --> 00:55:47,721
- You didn't push me?
- Ma'am, please.

733
00:55:47,929 --> 00:55:50,140
If I knew she were pregnant,

734
00:55:50,306 --> 00:55:53,768
I wouldn't even have tried to get
her out of the house.

735
00:55:54,394 --> 00:55:56,271
I just wanted to close the door.

736
00:55:56,646 --> 00:55:58,273
Do you accept his explanation?

737
00:55:58,440 --> 00:56:02,318
He didn't push. He grabbed me here
and threw me and I fell on the stairs.

738
00:56:02,569 --> 00:56:04,612
I didn't throw you.

739
00:56:04,779 --> 00:56:07,449
I wanted to get you out of my house.

740
00:56:07,657 --> 00:56:10,577
- Who throws out a pregnant woman?
- I didn't know.

741
00:56:10,785 --> 00:56:11,828
Why are you lying?

742
00:56:11,911 --> 00:56:14,122
I found out in the hospital.

743
00:56:14,748 --> 00:56:17,292
Your Honor, can't everyone tell

744
00:56:17,500 --> 00:56:20,628
from the body of a woman
that she is pregnant?

745
00:56:21,129 --> 00:56:22,289
Four to five months pregnant.

746
00:56:22,338 --> 00:56:24,007
When would I even see you?

747
00:56:24,257 --> 00:56:27,260
I was already gone
or leaving when she'd come.

748
00:56:27,427 --> 00:56:30,346
When I'd come, she looked like this.

749
00:56:30,513 --> 00:56:32,849
Always with the chador.

750
00:56:33,016 --> 00:56:34,768
How can anyone tell she was pregnant?

751
00:56:34,934 --> 00:56:37,103
He can claim that he couldn't guess.

752
00:56:37,604 --> 00:56:41,483
I didn't think a pregnant woman
would come for this kind of work.

753
00:56:42,776 --> 00:56:45,862
Your Honor, I spoke of my pregnancy

754
00:56:46,112 --> 00:56:49,324
in front of him, his
daughter and her tutor.

755
00:56:49,532 --> 00:56:51,618
They all heard it.

756
00:56:51,785 --> 00:56:53,661
When? I don't remember.

757
00:56:53,828 --> 00:56:55,705
No, of course you wouldn't remember.

758
00:56:55,872 --> 00:56:58,666
The issue isn't that I knew or not.

759
00:56:58,875 --> 00:57:00,376
Yes.

760
00:57:00,627 --> 00:57:02,295
If it's proven that you knew,

761
00:57:02,462 --> 00:57:04,839
the court can request
a prison term of one to three years.

762
00:57:08,051 --> 00:57:09,511
- Well?
- What?

763
00:57:10,553 --> 00:57:12,180
No, I didn't know.

764
00:57:12,347 --> 00:57:15,391
His daughter's tutor can testify.

765
00:57:15,558 --> 00:57:16,976
Can she come in tomorrow?

766
00:57:17,143 --> 00:57:19,521
I don't want her or the school involved.

767
00:57:19,687 --> 00:57:22,023
It's not good for my daughter.

768
00:57:22,190 --> 00:57:24,859
You trash. You've killed my child.

769
00:57:25,026 --> 00:57:26,361
It's bad for your child?

770
00:57:26,528 --> 00:57:30,115
She matters but ours was an animal?

771
00:57:30,198 --> 00:57:34,869
- Don't insult...
- Am I insulting? He took my pregnant wife...

772
00:57:35,078 --> 00:57:36,371
Quiet or I'll put you in prison.

773
00:57:36,871 --> 00:57:39,374
Please, he's a bit hot-tempered.

774
00:57:40,375 --> 00:57:42,544
Hot-tempered?

775
00:57:42,752 --> 00:57:47,507
I should sue you for working for
a single man we don't even know.

776
00:57:47,715 --> 00:57:51,553
I wanted to help with the bills.
He hasn't worked for months.

777
00:57:52,345 --> 00:57:54,889
The tutor has to come in as a witness.

778
00:57:55,098 --> 00:57:57,725
Call her to come in tomorrow.

779
00:58:00,353 --> 00:58:03,690
Your Honor, I'm here today for one thing.

780
00:58:04,190 --> 00:58:07,068
I lost my child but it didn't hurt as much

781
00:58:07,235 --> 00:58:10,071
as when he accused me of being a thief.

782
00:58:10,238 --> 00:58:11,322
We're thieves?

783
00:58:11,406 --> 00:58:12,824
If we were thieves,

784
00:58:12,907 --> 00:58:16,244
we wouldn't come to wipe your father's ass.

785
00:58:16,411 --> 00:58:18,913
Do you have proof that she stole?

786
00:58:19,080 --> 00:58:20,415
I didn't say she stole.

787
00:58:20,790 --> 00:58:23,084
Money was missing

788
00:58:23,543 --> 00:58:26,045
and it was the same amount that I pay her.

789
00:58:26,254 --> 00:58:27,255
Is that why you fought?

790
00:58:27,547 --> 00:58:29,048
He accused her of stealing.

791
00:58:29,257 --> 00:58:32,093
Your Honor, my father has Alzheimer's.

792
00:58:32,594 --> 00:58:36,389
She tied his hand to the bed
and left the house.

793
00:58:36,764 --> 00:58:38,266
That day I came home early.

794
00:58:38,433 --> 00:58:41,144
I saw him on the floor with his hand tied.

795
00:58:41,394 --> 00:58:42,770
I thought he had died.

796
00:58:43,438 --> 00:58:47,775
She came back
and I'm not saying I wasn't angry,

797
00:58:47,859 --> 00:58:48,860
I was.

798
00:58:48,943 --> 00:58:51,613
I told her to leave and she wouldn't.

799
00:58:51,821 --> 00:58:53,781
Where should I have gone?

800
00:58:53,948 --> 00:58:55,450
He accused me of stealing.

801
00:58:55,617 --> 00:58:58,244
If I hadn't asked for the money and left,

802
00:58:58,411 --> 00:59:00,580
he would've thought I had stolen.

803
00:59:00,788 --> 00:59:02,123
Sit down.

804
00:59:02,582 --> 00:59:04,626
- Was your father hurt?
- Yes, he was.

805
00:59:04,834 --> 00:59:08,463
How hurt? If he had been, he
would've filed a complaint.

806
00:59:08,630 --> 00:59:09,964
Yes, he was hurt.

807
00:59:10,131 --> 00:59:11,591
Where are you going?

808
00:59:11,758 --> 00:59:15,011
I'm going to check on my child.

809
00:59:15,345 --> 00:59:16,387
Come back quick.

810
00:59:16,638 --> 00:59:17,972
Close the door.

811
01:00:01,557 --> 01:00:02,684
What's taking so long?

812
01:00:03,768 --> 01:00:06,854
I'm not well. You go, I'll come.

813
01:00:07,063 --> 01:00:08,856
He says you locked up his father and left.

814
01:00:10,858 --> 01:00:11,859
What should I say?

815
01:00:12,360 --> 01:00:14,612
Say? If he complains you'll be charged.

816
01:00:16,781 --> 01:00:18,283
Where's Somayeh?

817
01:00:18,866 --> 01:00:19,951
Over there.

818
01:00:20,201 --> 01:00:22,036
Go. I'll get her and come.

819
01:00:22,620 --> 01:00:23,871
Let's go.

820
01:00:41,222 --> 01:00:42,390
Yes?

821
01:00:44,392 --> 01:00:47,478
He was sleeping.
I locked the door to keep him in.

822
01:00:47,895 --> 01:00:52,108
Even he would lock the door
and leave me the key.

823
01:00:52,275 --> 01:00:53,651
I saw that he does it so I...

824
01:00:53,818 --> 01:00:55,820
He says you tied him to the bed.

825
01:00:58,656 --> 01:01:02,452
I was afraid he would wake up
and do something to himself.

826
01:01:02,618 --> 01:01:05,663
I was afraid for him.

827
01:01:05,913 --> 01:01:08,124
Why did you leave?

828
01:01:08,291 --> 01:01:10,335
- So you should hit her?
- Quiet!

829
01:01:10,585 --> 01:01:12,420
Who said you could touch my wife?

830
01:01:12,503 --> 01:01:13,588
Sir, get out.

831
01:01:13,671 --> 01:01:16,090
They don't care about honor, I do.

832
01:01:16,424 --> 01:01:18,968
- Don't be offensive.
- Leave the room.

833
01:01:22,430 --> 01:01:24,349
I want to file a complaint
against this woman.

834
01:01:24,474 --> 01:01:25,516
Write your complaint.

835
01:01:25,767 --> 01:01:29,354
Take your father to the medical examiner.
If he's hurt get a report.

836
01:01:29,520 --> 01:01:31,272
What happens to our complaint?

837
01:01:31,689 --> 01:01:33,358
Sign this and leave.

838
01:01:33,691 --> 01:01:35,360
You have to post bail.

839
01:01:35,485 --> 01:01:36,778
What for?

840
01:01:37,278 --> 01:01:39,822
You're charged with murder.

841
01:01:39,989 --> 01:01:41,991
I can't let you leave.

842
01:01:42,158 --> 01:01:44,702
The blood money is 40 million.

843
01:01:44,869 --> 01:01:46,996
How am I going to post bail?

844
01:01:47,622 --> 01:01:51,125
I live at my dad's. He has Alzheimer's.

845
01:01:51,501 --> 01:01:53,378
If you don't you'll go to jail.

846
01:01:53,544 --> 01:01:56,714
My father can't even come here.

847
01:01:56,964 --> 01:01:58,383
He's sick.

848
01:01:58,549 --> 01:01:59,801
Please don't.

849
01:01:59,967 --> 01:02:02,387
I can't go to jail.

850
01:02:02,637 --> 01:02:04,889
I've left him at home to come here.

851
01:02:05,390 --> 01:02:07,308
I can't go to jail.

852
01:02:07,475 --> 01:02:08,810
I can't post bail.

853
01:02:08,976 --> 01:02:10,603
It's not in my hands. It's the law.

854
01:02:10,686 --> 01:02:11,896
Wait one second.

855
01:02:11,979 --> 01:02:14,690
What should I do with my dad?

856
01:02:14,899 --> 01:02:18,152
I left him at home
and locked the door to come here.

857
01:02:18,319 --> 01:02:19,904
My child will come home from school.

858
01:02:20,071 --> 01:02:21,364
Please. What are you writing?

859
01:02:21,489 --> 01:02:24,325
Don't waste time. Go make your call.

860
01:02:24,492 --> 01:02:26,536
I can't go to jail. I won't go.

861
01:02:27,078 --> 01:02:28,496
Write what you want!

862
01:02:28,704 --> 01:02:29,747
Go get an officer.

863
01:02:30,164 --> 01:02:31,874
What for? Don't.

864
01:02:32,041 --> 01:02:34,502
I'm begging you.

865
01:02:34,669 --> 01:02:36,504
Please don't write it.

866
01:02:37,255 --> 01:02:40,091
My life will be ruined.

867
01:02:40,258 --> 01:02:42,677
Don't waste time. Go make your call.

868
01:02:45,513 --> 01:02:49,392
Hello, Termeh. I'm stuck here.
They're keeping me tonight.

869
01:02:49,559 --> 01:02:53,563
Don't worry. It's nothing.
But you'll be alone tonight.

870
01:02:53,729 --> 01:02:57,692
Take care of the house.
Take Grandpa to the bathroom regularly.

871
01:02:57,859 --> 01:03:00,027
Take care of yourself.
I'll call you tomorrow.

872
01:03:32,768 --> 01:03:36,397
If you hadn't left, Dad
wouldn't be in jail.

873
01:03:36,564 --> 01:03:38,941
Your dad's not in jail because of me.

874
01:03:39,942 --> 01:03:41,736
He hit a pregnant woman.

875
01:03:41,903 --> 01:03:43,488
She came 'cause you left.

876
01:03:44,322 --> 01:03:46,449
How upset he was that I left.

877
01:03:47,241 --> 01:03:49,577
He knew you weren't really leaving.

878
01:03:50,912 --> 01:03:52,497
Did you tell him?

879
01:03:52,580 --> 01:03:53,956
No, he knew.

880
01:03:54,999 --> 01:03:56,167
Tell me the truth.

881
01:03:56,334 --> 01:03:57,752
You told him?

882
01:04:05,510 --> 01:04:08,346
Get your stuff. We're going to Grandma's.

883
01:04:08,429 --> 01:04:09,680
What about Grandpa?

884
01:04:09,764 --> 01:04:11,057
We'll take him, too.

885
01:04:11,140 --> 01:04:13,184
I have homework. I'm not coming.

886
01:04:13,976 --> 01:04:16,521
- You'll be on your own...
- Fine.

887
01:04:17,772 --> 01:04:20,441
You'd better not call.

888
01:04:31,869 --> 01:04:34,664
He doesn't even ask me to stay.

889
01:04:35,206 --> 01:04:37,124
He doesn't refuse to divorce.

890
01:04:37,667 --> 01:04:41,295
After having lived together for 14 years.

891
01:05:23,254 --> 01:05:24,255
Dad!

892
01:05:27,008 --> 01:05:29,010
What are you doing here?

893
01:05:30,177 --> 01:05:31,679
Who are you with?

894
01:05:32,888 --> 01:05:35,349
Didn't you have an exam?

895
01:05:35,516 --> 01:05:37,184
No, it's tomorrow.

896
01:05:37,893 --> 01:05:39,520
Who are you with?

897
01:05:44,066 --> 01:05:45,192
Hello.

898
01:05:46,027 --> 01:05:48,529
Shouldn't you tell us you're in trouble

899
01:05:48,613 --> 01:05:50,364
so we can bail you out?

900
01:05:50,531 --> 01:05:52,199
I didn't want to trouble you.

901
01:05:52,366 --> 01:05:53,909
Silly man.

902
01:05:54,118 --> 01:05:56,120
- Sit.
- No, ma'am, he has a hearing.

903
01:06:00,124 --> 01:06:01,584
Where's Grandpa?

904
01:06:01,709 --> 01:06:03,210
He's safe.

905
01:06:03,711 --> 01:06:06,255
What are they saying?

906
01:06:06,922 --> 01:06:10,217
"My child" as if their 18-year old son

907
01:06:10,384 --> 01:06:12,219
was stabbed to death.

908
01:06:12,386 --> 01:06:13,721
Did you speak to them?

909
01:06:13,888 --> 01:06:16,557
You can't even speak to the man.

910
01:06:16,724 --> 01:06:19,268
I told the wife, "You're young.

911
01:06:19,602 --> 01:06:21,312
"You can try next year."

912
01:06:24,899 --> 01:06:25,900
What happened?

913
01:06:25,983 --> 01:06:28,986
- I have to appraise the house.
- Okay, go.

914
01:06:29,153 --> 01:06:30,446
Hi.

915
01:06:30,780 --> 01:06:33,074
- I'll be back.
- We'll be here.

916
01:06:38,746 --> 01:06:39,955
Thanks.

917
01:06:42,917 --> 01:06:44,585
- Hi, Mrs. Lavasani.
- Hi, how are you?

918
01:06:44,752 --> 01:06:45,836
Good, you?

919
01:06:46,003 --> 01:06:49,298
- Sorry we're troubling you.
- No, what trouble?

920
01:06:49,465 --> 01:06:53,010
Is it true what they're saying?

921
01:06:53,177 --> 01:06:56,430
Yes, unfortunately he pushed her
and she fell and lost her baby.

922
01:06:57,139 --> 01:06:58,349
So what should I tell them?

923
01:06:58,933 --> 01:07:01,477
I don't know what they'll ask.

924
01:07:01,644 --> 01:07:04,689
What if he asks something
to his disadvantage?

925
01:07:06,273 --> 01:07:08,609
I think you should tell the truth.

926
01:07:08,693 --> 01:07:09,860
Please don't stand there.

927
01:07:10,486 --> 01:07:11,696
Where was he?

928
01:07:11,862 --> 01:07:13,864
Mr. Lavasani was in the kitchen.

929
01:07:14,031 --> 01:07:17,326
He didn't have a reaction
to your conversation?

930
01:07:17,493 --> 01:07:18,619
If he did I didn't notice.

931
01:07:19,203 --> 01:07:21,205
How did you realize she was pregnant?

932
01:07:22,289 --> 01:07:23,999
I think she told me.

933
01:07:24,625 --> 01:07:26,335
You asked. Why should I tell you?

934
01:07:28,295 --> 01:07:32,174
Her daughter was drawing
a man and a woman.

935
01:07:32,341 --> 01:07:33,781
She said this is my mommy and daddy.

936
01:07:34,176 --> 01:07:37,138
I said your mommy's not that fat.
She said she was pregnant.

937
01:07:37,304 --> 01:07:39,223
So it wasn't from her appearance?

938
01:07:39,390 --> 01:07:40,474
No.

939
01:07:40,683 --> 01:07:41,726
Why are you lying?

940
01:07:42,309 --> 01:07:43,477
You're a woman.

941
01:07:43,644 --> 01:07:47,022
You can't tell if a woman is pregnant?

942
01:07:47,231 --> 01:07:49,483
Even if I could tell,

943
01:07:49,650 --> 01:07:52,653
what difference does it make
for Mr. Lavasani?

944
01:07:53,320 --> 01:07:55,489
This woman is his daughter's tutor.

945
01:07:55,656 --> 01:07:57,408
They've fixed their story.

946
01:07:57,658 --> 01:07:59,160
Why are you insulting this lady?

947
01:07:59,368 --> 01:08:00,995
No one's talking to you.

948
01:08:01,537 --> 01:08:03,417
When did I have the opportunity
to fix my story?

949
01:08:03,497 --> 01:08:04,707
I was here last night.

950
01:08:05,082 --> 01:08:08,002
One thing is clear. Now
that we are speaking,

951
01:08:08,335 --> 01:08:11,922
that man over there can hear us, can't he?

952
01:08:12,173 --> 01:08:13,507
I didn't hear you.

953
01:08:14,341 --> 01:08:18,345
My mind is on other things.

954
01:08:19,180 --> 01:08:22,266
Why would I listen to your conversation?

955
01:08:22,516 --> 01:08:23,934
Do I have to swear to God?

956
01:08:24,518 --> 01:08:25,770
Like you believe in God!

957
01:08:26,020 --> 01:08:27,855
No, God is for your type only!

958
01:08:28,230 --> 01:08:29,940
Open that window.

959
01:08:32,234 --> 01:08:33,778
He is an honorable man.

960
01:08:33,944 --> 01:08:36,363
I've been going there for a year
to teach his daughter.

961
01:08:37,531 --> 01:08:39,200
He's not like that.

962
01:08:39,533 --> 01:08:42,787
Why should she hide her pregnancy?

963
01:08:43,037 --> 01:08:45,873
If I knew I wouldn't have hired her.

964
01:08:46,040 --> 01:08:49,418
Why did you hire her
without her husband's permission?

965
01:08:50,044 --> 01:08:51,045
Thank you.

966
01:08:51,378 --> 01:08:52,963
You may go.

967
01:08:53,130 --> 01:08:54,215
Thank you.

968
01:08:57,927 --> 01:09:03,724
"During the Sassanid period,
people were divided into two classes,

969
01:09:03,891 --> 01:09:06,227
"the royalty,

970
01:09:06,727 --> 01:09:10,481
"the upper class and the normal people."

971
01:09:10,648 --> 01:09:12,233
"The ordinary people."

972
01:09:16,987 --> 01:09:18,447
What did they ask you?

973
01:09:18,614 --> 01:09:22,493
Whether your dad knew she was pregnant.

974
01:09:22,660 --> 01:09:25,496
Forgive us for taking your time.

975
01:09:25,663 --> 01:09:28,958
There's nothing to forgive.

976
01:09:29,792 --> 01:09:32,086
Sweetie, how did mommy lose her baby?

977
01:09:32,253 --> 01:09:34,129
She got a tummy ache.

978
01:09:35,589 --> 01:09:37,424
Why?

979
01:09:38,092 --> 01:09:40,427
Did Daddy fight with her?

980
01:09:41,095 --> 01:09:43,639
Why should he fight with her?

981
01:09:43,806 --> 01:09:47,852
Maybe because she didn't tell him
she was working in people's homes?

982
01:09:48,018 --> 01:09:51,272
- Did he hit her?
- My mom and dad never fight.

983
01:09:51,939 --> 01:09:56,527
Then why were they fighting
in your drawing that day?

984
01:09:56,694 --> 01:09:58,153
You showed me.

985
01:09:58,320 --> 01:10:00,155
They don't fight anymore.

986
01:10:00,322 --> 01:10:01,949
No?

987
01:10:02,783 --> 01:10:04,326
You're sure?

988
01:10:08,706 --> 01:10:11,542
Yesterday he said
he didn't know she was pregnant.

989
01:10:11,709 --> 01:10:13,961
Now he says he didn't push her.

990
01:10:14,128 --> 01:10:16,547
And you just stand there in silence!

991
01:10:16,839 --> 01:10:19,300
Honestly, didn't you push me?

992
01:10:19,800 --> 01:10:21,468
- I didn't say I...
- Listen...

993
01:10:21,969 --> 01:10:23,846
Don't repeat everything.

994
01:10:24,805 --> 01:10:26,724
How far is the door from the stairs?

995
01:10:26,807 --> 01:10:27,933
2 meters?

996
01:10:28,017 --> 01:10:30,811
What else can have happened to her?

997
01:10:30,895 --> 01:10:32,229
The corridor in our house...

998
01:10:32,396 --> 01:10:33,856
- Look...
- I am talking!

999
01:10:34,064 --> 01:10:35,649
Don't talk. Just answer.

1000
01:10:35,858 --> 01:10:37,026
Quiet!

1001
01:10:37,818 --> 01:10:41,655
You've come here to answer.

1002
01:10:42,406 --> 01:10:44,325
I've a question for you to answer.

1003
01:10:44,491 --> 01:10:45,492
I want to ask him...

1004
01:10:45,701 --> 01:10:46,744
Ask me.

1005
01:10:46,827 --> 01:10:50,205
If you hadn't done anything wrong,
why'd you come to the hospital

1006
01:10:50,414 --> 01:10:52,333
to see what was wrong with her?

1007
01:10:52,499 --> 01:10:54,043
I came out of decency.

1008
01:10:54,251 --> 01:10:56,337
Where was your decency when you hit her?

1009
01:10:56,503 --> 01:10:58,172
Was anyone there during the fight?

1010
01:10:58,714 --> 01:11:00,007
Their neighbor was there.

1011
01:11:00,507 --> 01:11:01,717
I'll order questionings.

1012
01:11:01,884 --> 01:11:04,929
They're in it too just like the teacher.

1013
01:11:05,054 --> 01:11:07,222
He's been insulting me from the start!

1014
01:11:07,431 --> 01:11:09,183
Am I lying?

1015
01:11:09,350 --> 01:11:11,268
I'll determine who's lying or not.

1016
01:11:11,518 --> 01:11:12,770
You be quiet.

1017
01:11:12,937 --> 01:11:16,398
Sir, do you realize
his ex-wife has posted his bail?

1018
01:11:16,857 --> 01:11:17,858
Oh, my God!

1019
01:11:17,942 --> 01:11:19,401
Can someone vouch for you?

1020
01:11:19,610 --> 01:11:20,736
What do you mean?

1021
01:11:20,903 --> 01:11:23,864
A government employee
or business-owner to vouch for you.

1022
01:11:23,948 --> 01:11:25,783
- No one.
- Why vouch?

1023
01:11:26,033 --> 01:11:27,743
Because she's been accused.

1024
01:11:28,118 --> 01:11:29,203
Accused of what?

1025
01:11:29,620 --> 01:11:32,039
According to the complaint he filed...

1026
01:11:32,247 --> 01:11:33,374
Which he had no right...

1027
01:11:33,540 --> 01:11:36,961
She admitted that she tied his father
to the bed and locked him up.

1028
01:11:37,086 --> 01:11:38,128
I explained to you why.

1029
01:11:38,212 --> 01:11:39,588
Her child just died.

1030
01:11:39,755 --> 01:11:41,298
Keep your voice down.

1031
01:11:43,092 --> 01:11:45,803
Aren't you ashamed?
You call yourself a man?

1032
01:11:46,720 --> 01:11:48,055
I said quiet.

1033
01:11:50,724 --> 01:11:54,895
For God's sake, listen to us for a change.

1034
01:11:55,062 --> 01:11:57,147
He is twisting everything.

1035
01:11:57,815 --> 01:12:00,651
He beat my wife and she had a miscarriage.

1036
01:12:00,901 --> 01:12:03,779
What could be clearer?
Why are you being unjust?

1037
01:12:03,946 --> 01:12:05,072
Listen to us for a change.

1038
01:12:05,239 --> 01:12:08,409
If you disturb the peace,
I'll send you to jail for three days.

1039
01:12:09,159 --> 01:12:11,578
I've lost everything.
You think I fear jail?

1040
01:12:11,745 --> 01:12:13,330
You should fear God.

1041
01:12:14,915 --> 01:12:17,334
Mr. Izadi, call an officer to arrest him.

1042
01:12:17,584 --> 01:12:19,628
Sir, for the sake of the Quran, don't.

1043
01:12:20,754 --> 01:12:23,424
- No, let them come and take me.
- Go out. Be quiet.

1044
01:12:23,590 --> 01:12:26,593
Why be quiet?
So they can trample my rights?

1045
01:12:26,760 --> 01:12:27,928
Go out.

1046
01:12:28,345 --> 01:12:31,015
- Fine, I'm leaving.
- Sir, come out.

1047
01:12:32,641 --> 01:12:33,934
Let me get my helmet.

1048
01:12:34,101 --> 01:12:35,102
Get out.

1049
01:12:36,603 --> 01:12:39,273
I worked for ten years with a cobbler.

1050
01:12:39,440 --> 01:12:42,860
They fired me and said
get justice if you can.

1051
01:12:43,027 --> 01:12:48,198
I sued and went back and forth for a year.
In the end, nothing.

1052
01:12:48,365 --> 01:12:50,117
They said go sit at home.

1053
01:12:51,118 --> 01:12:53,037
But this time I won't let it go.

1054
01:12:53,287 --> 01:12:55,873
This time it's different.

1055
01:12:56,123 --> 01:12:58,834
I have nothing to lose.

1056
01:12:59,001 --> 01:13:01,962
The problem is I can't talk like this guy.

1057
01:13:02,129 --> 01:13:03,797
I am hot-tempered.

1058
01:13:04,298 --> 01:13:05,507
Don't!

1059
01:13:14,641 --> 01:13:15,809
Hojjat?

1060
01:13:17,811 --> 01:13:19,021
I don't feel well.

1061
01:13:20,064 --> 01:13:21,315
Go sit there.

1062
01:13:21,398 --> 01:13:22,399
Let's go!

1063
01:13:22,483 --> 01:13:25,319
- What do you want? He's calm.
- I have to take him.

1064
01:13:25,486 --> 01:13:27,821
I'm going to talk to the judge.

1065
01:13:27,988 --> 01:13:30,032
Stay there and don't move.

1066
01:13:36,413 --> 01:13:37,998
Sir...

1067
01:13:38,165 --> 01:13:39,500
I beg you...

1068
01:13:39,666 --> 01:13:41,001
