and now she wants to blame me.

1322
01:30:21,334 --> 01:30:24,003
Her child said that day
she had gone to the doctor.

1323
01:30:24,170 --> 01:30:27,840
Why couldn't she wait two hours
to go to the doctor?

1324
01:30:28,007 --> 01:30:30,510
Why did she tie the old man
to his bed and leave?

1325
01:30:30,676 --> 01:30:32,845
The examiner said
her child died due to a blow.

1326
01:30:33,012 --> 01:30:36,057
How do we know it was a blow from me?

1327
01:30:36,599 --> 01:30:39,685
I won't accept it till
it's been proven to me.

1328
01:30:42,271 --> 01:30:44,565
Fine, let me take Termeh.

1329
01:30:44,732 --> 01:30:48,194
Shame on you
for putting pressure on me now.

1330
01:30:48,361 --> 01:30:49,487
I am worried about her.

1331
01:30:49,570 --> 01:30:52,615
Your child wants to live here.
She has to stay here and learn.

1332
01:30:52,824 --> 01:30:55,118
Learn what? Fighting and obstinacy?

1333
01:30:55,284 --> 01:30:57,662
To learn not to be a coward like you

1334
01:30:57,829 --> 01:31:00,373
who gives in so easily.

1335
01:31:00,665 --> 01:31:03,835
He knows who to frighten.
Why doesn't he threaten me?

1336
01:31:04,043 --> 01:31:05,044
Yes, I'm a coward.

1337
01:31:05,711 --> 01:31:09,090
Your whole life,

1338
01:31:09,257 --> 01:31:11,634
instead of solving problems,

1339
01:31:11,843 --> 01:31:16,556
you've either run away or
raised your hands and given in.

1340
01:31:16,806 --> 01:31:20,351
Just say why you want
to leave this country.

1341
01:31:20,518 --> 01:31:21,811
You're afraid to stay.

1342
01:31:22,395 --> 01:31:25,314
I was gone one week
and you couldn't manage.

1343
01:31:25,398 --> 01:31:27,400
I couldn't manage and I'm responsible.

1344
01:31:28,442 --> 01:31:31,946
Give me Termeh and you do what you want.

1345
01:31:34,824 --> 01:31:37,243
Termeh, sweetie, you don't have to stay.

1346
01:31:37,326 --> 01:31:39,036
Go wherever you like.

1347
01:31:44,542 --> 01:31:46,502
You still don't want to come?

1348
01:31:57,722 --> 01:31:59,432
"He sells it for 20 a kilo.

1349
01:31:59,599 --> 01:32:03,603
"If every day he sells
270 kilos..." Write 270.

1350
01:32:05,980 --> 01:32:10,026
Then, how much profit
does he make in one day?

1351
01:32:11,027 --> 01:32:12,737
How do you solve this?

1352
01:32:13,237 --> 01:32:14,947
Did you lie?

1353
01:32:16,699 --> 01:32:17,867
What?

1354
01:32:19,368 --> 01:32:20,494
Did you lie?

1355
01:32:22,121 --> 01:32:23,331
About what?

1356
01:32:25,166 --> 01:32:28,669
When you said
you didn't know she was pregnant.

1357
01:32:29,921 --> 01:32:31,130
Why?

1358
01:32:32,882 --> 01:32:37,803
You said that you didn't hear Ms. Qahraei
and Razieh speaking.

1359
01:32:37,887 --> 01:32:38,888
Yes.

1360
01:32:39,555 --> 01:32:44,268
Then how did you know that
Ms. Qahraei gave her the number?

1361
01:32:45,311 --> 01:32:47,772
Didn't she say it at the same time?

1362
01:32:56,113 --> 01:32:57,823
Okay.

1363
01:32:59,033 --> 01:33:01,994
If we want to calculate the profit...

1364
01:33:07,959 --> 01:33:09,043
Yes, I knew.

1365
01:33:11,587 --> 01:33:13,631
Your mom was telling the truth.

1366
01:33:15,967 --> 01:33:21,055
When they were talking in the hall,
I heard everything from the kitchen.

1367
01:33:22,390 --> 01:33:24,392
Then why did you say you didn't?

1368
01:33:27,937 --> 01:33:30,940
Do you know what would happen
if I said I knew?

1369
01:33:34,193 --> 01:33:36,862
One and a half to three years in prison.

1370
01:33:38,155 --> 01:33:41,826
I only thought of what would happen to you,

1371
01:33:42,326 --> 01:33:44,120
who you'd stay with.

1372
01:33:45,079 --> 01:33:46,914
I said I didn't know.

1373
01:33:49,750 --> 01:33:51,752
If you knew, why did you hit her?

1374
01:33:51,919 --> 01:33:55,673
I knew she was pregnant
but at that moment I didn't.

1375
01:33:55,840 --> 01:33:58,718
I had forgotten it. I
wasn't paying attention.

1376
01:34:04,974 --> 01:34:06,934
So tell them this.

1377
01:34:10,771 --> 01:34:13,149
The law doesn't care about this.

1378
01:34:13,774 --> 01:34:16,235
Either I knew or I didn't...

1379
01:34:23,367 --> 01:34:24,660
Look at me.

1380
01:34:25,786 --> 01:34:28,414
If you want me to I'll tell them.

1381
01:35:21,926 --> 01:35:22,968
Hi.

1382
01:35:28,474 --> 01:35:31,018
Didn't I say not to come to the front?

1383
01:35:51,956 --> 01:35:53,207
Ms. Qahraei!

1384
01:36:04,927 --> 01:36:06,095
What are you doing?

1385
01:36:06,554 --> 01:36:09,014
Ms. Qahraei, wait...

1386
01:36:10,057 --> 01:36:13,853
If you pull over
I'll just explain something to you.

1387
01:36:14,311 --> 01:36:15,563
Please let me...

1388
01:36:17,022 --> 01:36:18,190
Dad!

1389
01:36:21,777 --> 01:36:23,537
Who's responsible for
my child's safety now?

1390
01:36:23,654 --> 01:36:25,322
Without a witness there's no case.

1391
01:36:25,489 --> 01:36:28,742
So without a witness
I should wait for him to kill her

1392
01:36:28,826 --> 01:36:30,286
and then come to you?

1393
01:36:30,494 --> 01:36:32,913
How should I know you
are telling the truth?

1394
01:36:33,080 --> 01:36:34,790
Why should I lie?

1395
01:36:34,999 --> 01:36:38,085
Bring my daughter and father here
just to lie?

1396
01:36:38,502 --> 01:36:40,546
- Is she here now?
- Yes, outside.

1397
01:36:40,629 --> 01:36:42,673
Ask her yourself.

1398
01:36:42,840 --> 01:36:47,261
I'm afraid to leave her at school.
I'm afraid to leave my dad at home.

1399
01:36:47,803 --> 01:36:49,388
Is the plaintiff here?

1400
01:36:50,723 --> 01:36:52,057
Did you finish writing?

1401
01:36:52,224 --> 01:36:53,309
Almost.

1402
01:36:54,268 --> 01:36:56,187
You didn't know his wife was pregnant?

1403
01:36:56,353 --> 01:36:57,605
No, I didn't.

1404
01:36:57,771 --> 01:37:01,275
When she was speaking to the tutor,
you didn't hear them?

1405
01:37:01,442 --> 01:37:02,526
No, I didn't.

1406
01:37:03,694 --> 01:37:05,070
You didn't, huh?

1407
01:37:05,779 --> 01:37:07,781
What I'm saying is...

1408
01:37:08,032 --> 01:37:10,451
The tutor came and revoked her testimony.

1409
01:37:11,076 --> 01:37:12,786
She says you knew.

1410
01:37:13,204 --> 01:37:15,664
- She said I knew?
- Yes, she came yesterday.

1411
01:37:15,831 --> 01:37:17,416
He threatened her...

1412
01:37:17,625 --> 01:37:19,752
Answer me. Did you hear her or not?

1413
01:37:19,919 --> 01:37:21,420
I said no.

1414
01:37:21,587 --> 01:37:23,631
How did you know
about the doctor's number?

1415
01:37:23,839 --> 01:37:25,049
My daughter told me.

1416
01:37:25,216 --> 01:37:26,467
What did she tell you?

1417
01:37:26,675 --> 01:37:28,844
That she got the number from her teacher.

1418
01:37:30,012 --> 01:37:31,889
Go tell her to come in.

1419
01:37:33,182 --> 01:37:34,517
Now?

1420
01:37:35,392 --> 01:37:36,852
And wait outside.

1421
01:37:37,853 --> 01:37:39,230
What question?

1422
01:37:43,943 --> 01:37:45,736
What does he want to ask?

1423
01:37:48,489 --> 01:37:50,616
I don't know. Give me that.

1424
01:37:58,332 --> 01:38:00,125
So what do you have to say?

1425
01:38:00,292 --> 01:38:02,002
You haven't asked me anything.

1426
01:38:02,795 --> 01:38:05,339
Didn't your dad tell you
what I want to ask you?

1427
01:38:05,631 --> 01:38:06,632
No.

1428
01:38:06,840 --> 01:38:08,133
What grade are you in school?

1429
01:38:08,634 --> 01:38:09,885
Sixth.

1430
01:38:10,052 --> 01:38:13,472
The day your tutor came to your house

1431
01:38:13,639 --> 01:38:16,475
and asked the lady about her pregnancy,

1432
01:38:17,059 --> 01:38:18,727
were you there?

1433
01:38:18,978 --> 01:38:22,690
Not then, I had gone to get my books.

1434
01:38:23,190 --> 01:38:27,653
Then how did you know she got the
doctor's number from your tutor?

1435
01:38:28,737 --> 01:38:32,408
She gave her the number later,
when she was leaving.

1436
01:38:32,575 --> 01:38:33,867
In front of you?

1437
01:38:34,368 --> 01:38:35,411
Yes.

1438
01:38:35,494 --> 01:38:36,996
Why didn't you tell your dad sooner?

1439
01:38:37,371 --> 01:38:38,372
What?

1440
01:38:38,664 --> 01:38:42,167
That she got the doctor's number
from your tutor.

1441
01:38:42,334 --> 01:38:45,337
I didn't think it was important
for my dad to know.

1442
01:38:47,840 --> 01:38:50,342
And did you tell your
dad or did he hear it?

1443
01:38:51,093 --> 01:38:54,888
That she gave the number? I told him.

1444
01:38:55,514 --> 01:38:57,516
- You told him?
- Yes.

1445
01:38:59,351 --> 01:39:00,519
Okay.

1446
01:39:51,737 --> 01:39:53,489
What crime did I commit?

1447
01:39:53,656 --> 01:39:54,740
Nothing. You're right.

1448
01:39:55,741 --> 01:39:57,660
He's not accepting his responsibility.

1449
01:39:57,826 --> 01:40:00,913
I admit that he's to blame,
but in the end what will happen?

1450
01:40:01,080 --> 01:40:05,626
One or two years in court
for a payment plan of the blood money.

1451
01:40:05,793 --> 01:40:08,087
But why? That's what upsets me.

1452
01:40:08,253 --> 01:40:10,172
Why do you think it's for the money?

1453
01:40:10,422 --> 01:40:11,674
When did I say such a thing?

1454
01:40:11,757 --> 01:40:16,345
You think I am a bum and my kid died
and I don't understand anything.

1455
01:40:16,512 --> 01:40:18,180
I never said anything like that.

1456
01:40:18,263 --> 01:40:19,932
Let's see what she's saying.

1457
01:40:20,474 --> 01:40:21,475
There's no other way.

1458
01:40:22,309 --> 01:40:24,436
Your child won't come back.

1459
01:40:24,603 --> 01:40:26,605
My husband won't get hanged.

1460
01:40:26,772 --> 01:40:29,149
Her husband didn't do it on purpose.

1461
01:40:29,775 --> 01:40:32,986
They're good people
for giving you a solution.

1462
01:40:33,153 --> 01:40:36,657
Take the money and settle it.
You can use it in your situation.

1463
01:40:36,949 --> 01:40:40,994
Right now we'll decide on an amount
and I'll get my husband's approval.

1464
01:40:42,788 --> 01:40:46,166
Now we have to get his approval?
For God's sake leave us alone.

1465
01:40:49,294 --> 01:40:51,463
You act like you don't need the money.

1466
01:40:51,630 --> 01:40:52,840
Take a look at yourself.

1467
01:40:53,006 --> 01:40:54,633
Don't let him go.

1468
01:40:58,804 --> 01:41:00,973
Wait a second. I want to talk to you.

1469
01:41:51,607 --> 01:41:52,941
Will you stay?

1470
01:41:55,694 --> 01:41:56,695
Mom...

1471
01:41:59,364 --> 01:42:01,366
Let me speak to him.

1472
01:42:11,043 --> 01:42:13,045
Come sit. I want to talk to you.

1473
01:42:15,589 --> 01:42:16,590
I can hear you.

1474
01:42:19,218 --> 01:42:22,471
I went and spoke to her husband today.

1475
01:42:23,222 --> 01:42:24,556
Sit down.

1476
01:42:35,400 --> 01:42:36,777
I managed

1477
01:42:36,985 --> 01:42:38,779
to get him to agree

1478
01:42:39,738 --> 01:42:42,241
to take 15 million instead of 40 million.

1479
01:42:42,407 --> 01:42:45,494
Three five-million checks
in exchange for his consent.

1480
01:42:45,911 --> 01:42:47,579
How dare you speak to him about money?

1481
01:42:48,497 --> 01:42:50,377
I can't handle the stress
of my child's safety.

1482
01:42:50,415 --> 01:42:51,959
You don't get it.

1483
01:42:52,125 --> 01:42:54,962
Just now when you were late,
I was worried sick.

1484
01:42:55,170 --> 01:42:57,756
Why are you interfering?

1485
01:42:58,757 --> 01:43:00,425
I didn't come here to fight.

1486
01:43:00,759 --> 01:43:02,761
Oh, God, why can't I make her understand?

1487
01:43:02,928 --> 01:43:06,515
Didn't you say it was my fault,
that I introduced her,

1488
01:43:06,765 --> 01:43:09,768
that if I hadn't left,
none of this would've happened?

1489
01:43:09,935 --> 01:43:11,436
So let me fix it, then.

1490
01:43:11,937 --> 01:43:15,107
If I pay, it means
I have accepted it was my fault.

1491
01:43:15,315 --> 01:43:16,358
But he has consented.

1492
01:43:16,441 --> 01:43:17,860
He won't let us be.

1493
01:43:18,110 --> 01:43:20,696
- He won't, anyway.
- Why should I bribe him?

1494
01:43:20,863 --> 01:43:22,447
Think of it as my dower money.

1495
01:43:23,115 --> 01:43:26,493
If I had to I would beg and borrow

1496
01:43:26,869 --> 01:43:28,662
to get your dower money.

1497
01:43:28,871 --> 01:43:31,623
But I don't have the money
to pay for extortion.

1498
01:43:31,832 --> 01:43:35,460
Our child is going through adolescence.
She is suffering.

1499
01:43:37,129 --> 01:43:41,884
So you understand
the sensitivity of her adolescence.

1500
01:43:42,217 --> 01:43:44,017
If she was suffering
she wouldn't have stayed.

1501
01:43:44,553 --> 01:43:46,471
Why do you think she stayed?

1502
01:43:47,222 --> 01:43:48,807
Did she choose you?

1503
01:43:50,642 --> 01:43:52,561
To keep us from separating.

1504
01:43:54,813 --> 01:43:56,565
She knows I won't go anywhere without her.

1505
01:43:59,192 --> 01:44:01,987
She is suffering but she doesn't show it.

1506
01:44:06,408 --> 01:44:08,994
Call them now and say I won't pay

1507
01:44:09,161 --> 01:44:11,997
until it's been proved to me
that I am responsible.

1508
01:44:12,164 --> 01:44:13,749
I'll sell my car.

1509
01:44:14,875 --> 01:44:16,501
Don't sell it for my sake.

1510
01:44:16,668 --> 01:44:18,086
It's not for you.

1511
01:44:18,253 --> 01:44:20,505
If your child is not worth...

1512
01:44:20,672 --> 01:44:23,675
Why are you talking nonsense?
Money's not the issue.

1513
01:44:23,884 --> 01:44:27,095
I won't rest till my child's safety
is guaranteed.

1514
01:44:27,512 --> 01:44:29,932
You don't have the right to do anything.

1515
01:44:30,098 --> 01:44:31,350
Understand?

1516
01:44:32,017 --> 01:44:34,770
If I had done nothing
you would be in prison.

1517
01:44:38,899 --> 01:44:41,443
Come to court and get back the bail.

1518
01:44:42,027 --> 01:44:44,279
I don't want to be out because of it.

1519
01:45:03,090 --> 01:45:04,257
Get up, Termeh.

1520
01:45:05,384 --> 01:45:06,551
Get up, let's go.

1521
01:45:06,718 --> 01:45:08,053
Get up, I tell you.

1522
01:45:08,220 --> 01:45:09,388
Mom, please.

1523
01:45:11,974 --> 01:45:13,600
I don't want you to stay here.

1524
01:45:13,976 --> 01:45:15,143
No, Mom, I won't let you.

1525
01:45:15,310 --> 01:45:19,147
Is 15 million more important
than your child's life?

1526
01:45:19,314 --> 01:45:20,732
I won't let you do this.

1527
01:45:20,899 --> 01:45:22,734
If your child is not important...

1528
01:45:22,901 --> 01:45:25,612
Mom, please listen, why are you doing this?

1529
01:45:25,779 --> 01:45:27,114
You said you would stay.

1530
01:45:27,280 --> 01:45:28,407
I was stupid!

1531
01:45:30,409 --> 01:45:32,035
Mom, please...

1532
01:45:32,119 --> 01:45:33,453
I'll wait in the car.

1533
01:45:44,631 --> 01:45:48,593
Go there for a few days
till your exams are finished.

1534
01:45:49,302 --> 01:45:50,971
Your grandparents are there.

1535
01:45:51,847 --> 01:45:53,473
You'll have more fun.

1536
01:45:53,765 --> 01:45:55,517
Didn't you say it's not serious?

1537
01:45:56,643 --> 01:45:58,145
It got serious.

1538
01:45:59,771 --> 01:46:00,939
Termeh...

1539
01:46:01,857 --> 01:46:02,941
Honey...

1540
01:46:05,027 --> 01:46:06,862
If you cry I'll cry, too.

1541
01:46:07,029 --> 01:46:09,448
Why won't you pay them
so she'll come back?

1542
01:46:10,032 --> 01:46:12,451
This has nothing to do
with her coming back.

1543
01:46:12,617 --> 01:46:14,995
It does. She had come to stay.

1544
01:46:15,203 --> 01:46:17,622
Her stuff was in the car, I saw it.

1545
01:46:58,080 --> 01:47:01,333
If you think I am guilty, go get your mom.

1546
01:47:01,500 --> 01:47:04,002
We'll call them and go pay them.

1547
01:48:20,912 --> 01:48:22,289
I have doubts.

1548
01:48:22,455 --> 01:48:24,040
Didn't he throw you?

1549
01:48:24,791 --> 01:48:25,792
Yes.

1550
01:48:26,918 --> 01:48:28,920
Did something happen at home?

1551
01:48:30,422 --> 01:48:32,424
No. Even before, my child wasn't moving.

1552
01:48:34,092 --> 01:48:35,635
Before he threw you?

1553
01:48:41,766 --> 01:48:43,977
You mean your child had already died?

1554
01:48:44,811 --> 01:48:47,147
I don't know. Maybe.

1555
01:48:47,314 --> 01:48:48,940
Had something happened?

1556
01:48:51,276 --> 01:48:54,946
I'm not sure, but the
night before, I had pain.

1557
01:48:56,489 --> 01:48:58,950
- Have you ever lost a baby before?
- No.

1558
01:49:02,287 --> 01:49:03,663
I was hit by a car.

1559
01:49:10,962 --> 01:49:14,466
Your father-in-law had
gone into the street.

1560
01:49:14,633 --> 01:49:16,009
I went after him.

1561
01:49:17,302 --> 01:49:19,763
He was crossing the street to come back.

1562
01:49:19,930 --> 01:49:23,975
I ran to stop him but I got hit instead.

1563
01:49:24,684 --> 01:49:26,645
The pain started that night.

1564
01:49:29,856 --> 01:49:31,191
Does your husband know this?

1565
01:49:33,652 --> 01:49:35,612
Why don't you come say this in court?

1566
01:49:38,281 --> 01:49:42,118
My husband will kill me
if he finds out I told you this.

1567
01:49:43,662 --> 01:49:46,831
Since yesterday
when he promised his creditors,

1568
01:49:46,998 --> 01:49:48,166
he's been waiting.

1569
01:49:49,501 --> 01:49:53,046
What do we have to do with all this?

1570
01:49:56,299 --> 01:49:57,884
It's my fault.

1571
01:50:01,972 --> 01:50:05,850
Yesterday when he said
you'd promised him this money,

1572
01:50:06,017 --> 01:50:08,520
I got really scared. I called a few people.

1573
01:50:09,145 --> 01:50:11,856
They say if I have doubts
then it's a sin to take it.

1574
01:50:13,358 --> 01:50:16,194
If we don't pay
my husband's innocence must be proved.

1575
01:50:16,695 --> 01:50:20,198
I made you swear not to repeat any of this!

1576
01:50:20,365 --> 01:50:22,492
But your husband won't leave us alone.

1577
01:50:23,034 --> 01:50:24,411
I fear for my child.

1578
01:50:24,577 --> 01:50:29,165
I'm afraid that if I take this money,
something will happen to my child.

1579
01:50:29,332 --> 01:50:31,042
What do you want me to do?

1580
01:50:32,544 --> 01:50:34,170
Don't pay this money.

1581
01:50:35,588 --> 01:50:36,589
Don't.

1582
01:50:44,389 --> 01:50:46,558
Will your husband leave us alone?

1583
01:51:19,799 --> 01:51:22,552
Give me that. Bring some plates.

1584
01:51:23,595 --> 01:51:25,930
Don't worry. Nothing will happen.

1585
01:51:47,077 --> 01:51:50,080
When you revoke your complaint,

1586
01:51:50,288 --> 01:51:53,416
we'll give you these three checks.

1587
01:51:53,583 --> 01:51:54,918
God bless you.

1588
01:51:55,001 --> 01:51:59,923
Hojjat, get a pen and paper so we can
write everything down and sign it.

1589
01:52:01,132 --> 01:52:02,467
I want to say something first...

1590
01:52:02,634 --> 01:52:04,469
Say a prayer and finish it.

1591
01:52:04,636 --> 01:52:07,806
I have already agreed
and will honor my word.

1592
01:52:07,972 --> 01:52:13,269
I just want his wife
and my daughter to be here when I speak.

1593
01:52:15,814 --> 01:52:17,107
Where is she?

1594
01:52:19,526 --> 01:52:20,860
Thank you.

1595
01:52:21,778 --> 01:52:23,321
Please, also call my daughter.

1596
01:52:27,659 --> 01:52:29,786
Come in. Your father wants you.

1597
01:52:39,838 --> 01:52:41,673
Termeh, come and sit here.

1598
01:52:42,006 --> 01:52:43,675
Excuse me, sir.

1599
01:52:54,686 --> 01:52:56,187
Look...

1600
01:52:56,354 --> 01:52:59,566
I wrote the checks and
I'll give them to you.

1601
01:53:00,150 --> 01:53:01,484
There's no problem.

1602
01:53:01,901 --> 01:53:03,194
I need to ask a favor.

1603
01:53:04,571 --> 01:53:07,031
Ma'am, you are a devout person.

1604
01:53:08,199 --> 01:53:11,703
Swear on the Quran
that I caused your miscarriage.

1605
01:53:20,837 --> 01:53:21,838
Bring a Quran.

1606
01:53:22,881 --> 01:53:24,340
Go get it.

1607
01:53:41,608 --> 01:53:44,360
Come quickly or they'll suspect something.

1608
01:53:45,778 --> 01:53:48,114
His creditors are here for the money.

1609
01:53:48,281 --> 01:53:50,283
You'll ruin our reputation.

1610
01:53:52,410 --> 01:53:54,287
I won't swear.

1611
01:53:55,788 --> 01:53:59,751
Didn't you say you went to get his father
and a car hit you?

1612
01:54:01,419 --> 01:54:03,087
Why aren't you coming?

1613
01:54:04,214 --> 01:54:05,924
She's afraid to swear.

1614
01:54:07,133 --> 01:54:08,259
Why?

1615
01:54:08,426 --> 01:54:12,055
I... I have doubts.

1616
01:54:18,061 --> 01:54:19,270
Oh, God...

1617
01:54:20,939 --> 01:54:22,732
Azam, go sit with them.

1618
01:54:26,444 --> 01:54:30,323
Why are you saying this now?

1619
01:54:30,949 --> 01:54:33,284
I swear I told Azam.

1620
01:54:34,619 --> 01:54:37,163
Tell me exactly what happened.

1621
01:54:40,291 --> 01:54:43,127
The day before, a car hit me.

1622
01:54:43,753 --> 01:54:46,422
And that night I had a lot of pain.

1623
01:54:56,307 --> 01:54:58,810
- Let's go, it'll be my sin.
- No.

1624
01:54:59,435 --> 01:55:00,853
It's a sin. I asked.

1625
01:55:01,020 --> 01:55:03,982
What sin? He's consented. Let's go.

1626
01:55:04,148 --> 01:55:07,110
I am scared we'll be punished.

1627
01:55:07,277 --> 01:55:10,488
More punished than this?
Look at my situation.

1628
01:55:10,655 --> 01:55:14,200
Have mercy on me. On our child.

1629
01:55:14,367 --> 01:55:17,954
I'm afraid of something happening
to our child.

1630
01:55:18,371 --> 01:55:19,622
Let's go.

1631
01:55:19,789 --> 01:55:20,873
I can't.

1632
01:55:21,040 --> 01:55:22,333
Let's go.

1633
01:55:25,169 --> 01:55:26,796
I can't.

1634
01:55:31,175 --> 01:55:33,344
Don't hit yourself!

1635
01:55:52,822 --> 01:55:56,701
Why did you come here tonight?
Didn't I tell you not to come?

1636
01:55:57,493 --> 01:55:59,704
Didn't I say we don't want your money?

1637
01:56:00,163 --> 01:56:02,540
How will I live in this house?

1638
01:56:03,708 --> 01:56:06,210
Why did you do this to me?

1639
01:57:33,631 --> 01:57:34,674
Come on.

1640
01:57:39,971 --> 01:57:41,472
Let's go.

1641
01:57:57,530 --> 01:57:58,990
Hello. Come in.

1642
01:58:09,041 --> 01:58:10,835
So what's your decision?

1643
01:58:11,502 --> 01:58:16,799
Your parents have left it up to you
to decide who you want to live with.

1644
01:58:16,966 --> 01:58:19,510
With your father or your mother?

1645
01:58:21,012 --> 01:58:22,388
Have you decided?

1646
01:58:22,513 --> 01:58:23,556
Yes.

1647
01:58:24,140 --> 01:58:25,850
- Have you?
- Yes.

1648
01:58:36,694 --> 01:58:38,362
Have you decided or not?

1649
01:58:38,529 --> 01:58:39,530
Yes.

1650
01:58:42,033 --> 01:58:43,659
And what is it?

1651
01:58:45,495 --> 01:58:47,330
Do I have to say it now?

1652
01:58:48,539 --> 01:58:51,375
- If you haven't decided...
- Yes, I have.

1653
01:58:55,922 --> 01:58:58,466
- If you haven't decided yet...
- I have.

1654
01:58:58,549 --> 01:58:59,550
And?

1655
01:59:00,885 --> 01:59:03,721
Would you prefer them to wait outside?

1656
01:59:05,056 --> 01:59:06,516
Can they?

1657
01:59:07,558 --> 01:59:09,685
Sir, wait outside for a minute.

1658
01:59:11,854 --> 01:59:12,855
You, too, ma'am.

